description:
Flea and tick protection for dogs and puppies over 18 pounds.
Long-lasting collar kills and repels fleas for 8 months.
Starts working quickly to kill and repel fleas on contact, so pests don’t have to bite your dog to die.
Hassle-free, non-greasy and easy to use.
No prescription required.
